io.github.nixtabyte.telegram.jtelebot.server.impl

Class AbstractCommandTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • io.github.nixtabyte.telegram.jtelebot.server.impl.AbstractCommandTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandTask, Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultCommandTask

    public abstract class AbstractCommandTask
extends Observable
implements CommandTask, Runnable
    Abstract component that extends Observable and implements CommandTask and Runnable in order to handle the execution of every individual Command into a separated runnable thread.

    It allows to notify all Observer classes when it has finished processing the corresponding Command.
    Since:
    0.0.1
    See Also:
    Command, CommandTask, Observable, Runnable
